  <title translate="true">MT-POP-Next Segment</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword translate="true">Motion Definition:<keyword translate="true">Next Segment</keyword></keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="2" style="width:500px;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:189px;">
          <para styleclass="Image Caption"><image src="MT-NextSegment.ipp" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box" style="text-align:center;"><text styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Next-Segment</text><image src="Red-14-1b.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold;" translate="true"> is </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box" style="text-align:center;"><text styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold;" translate="true">AFTER the </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box" style="text-align:center;"><text styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Selected-Segment</text><image src="Red-14-2.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true">Next-Segment</text><image src="Red-14-1b.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> - the segment </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">after</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> (later-than, to the right of) the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-POP-Selected-Segment" styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Selected-Segment</link><image src="Red-14-2.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;"/></para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso-small"><text styleclass="SeeAlso-small" translate="true">See also: </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-POP-Previous-Segment" styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Previous-Segment</link><text styleclass="SeeAlso-small" translate="true">, </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-POP-Selected-Segment" styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Selected-Segment</link><text styleclass="SeeAlso-small" translate="true">.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;"/></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box2"><text styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true">NOTES</text><text styleclass="Notes" translate="true">:</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">1: If the </text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Selected-Segment</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true">is</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> the </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">last</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> (right-most)segment, then the </text><text styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true">Next-Segment</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> is the </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">first </text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">(left-most) segment of the motion.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">2: Of course, the </text><text styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true">Next-Segment</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> instantly becomes the </text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Selected-Segment</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> when you select it!</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
